name: Sky High
body:
### Sky High
This is the final project for COMP 50-GD, developed for Android using the pygame subset.  It works with Android version 2.x.

Developers:
@amandamb, @TZEYBE01, @gsiu

### To Run the Game
Download and unzip the file (or clone the directory). Then run the following code:

```
$ xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxcd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
